overview: A night in the life of a young adult celebrating her birthday with friends. Amidst the celebration, she encounters uncanny happenings and grows increasingly unnerved by a phantom-like presence. What she doesn’t discover, however, is a parallel existence –– a shadowed life on the fringes; a party of one.
tagline: A shadowed life on the fringes; a party of one.
title: Party of One
